PV PHP and FrankenPHP artifact recipe metadata
==============================================

This recipe packages PHP source archives listed in tracks.toml for standalone
PHP artifacts.

This recipe packages FrankenPHP source archives listed in tracks.toml for
FrankenPHP artifacts.

This product includes PHP software, freely available from
<http://www.php.net/software/>.

FrankenPHP is built from the php/frankenphp project:
https://github.com/php/frankenphp

Artifact-specific resource, track, version, source URL, and source checksum
fields are appended by build.sh when the archive is produced.
